%% Data Flow Diagram: LM Evaluation Harness
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.2/lm-evaluation-harness.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as TrustyAI LMEval Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant LMES as LMES Job Pod<br/>User 65532 (non-root)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Tracking<br/>HTTP/HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Evaluation Job Execution
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job + ConfigMap<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>LMES: Pod scheduled<br/>ConfigMap mounted at /meta/job.json

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (file-mounted)
    EvalHub-->>LMES: 200 OK

    LMES->>HFHub: GET tokenizer + datasets<br/>Auth: HF Token (optional)
    HFHub-->>LMES: Tokenizer + benchmark data

    loop For each evaluation batch
        LMES->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)
        Model-->>LMES: Completion responses
    end

    Note over LMES: Compute metrics<br/>(accuracy, BLEU, ROUGE, F1, etc.)

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST results + metrics<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>LMES: 200 OK

    Note over LMES,OCI: Flow 2: OCI Artifact Persistence
    Note over LMES: Save results to /opt/app-root/src/output/
    Note over LMES: olot packages to /tmp/oci-layout

    LMES->>OCI: skopeo copy oci-layout → registry<br/>Auth: Registry credentials
    OCI-->>LMES: Push complete

    LMES->>MLflow: Log metrics, parameters, artifacts<br/>Auth: configurable
    MLflow-->>LMES: 200 OK

    LMES->>EvalHub: POST status: COMPLETE<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>LMES: 200 OK
